## Columns

### `@mutate()`

The purpose of `@mutate()` is to add new colums that are calculated from existing colums. 

::: {.cell execution_count=13}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
@chain penguins begin
    @mutate(
        bill_ratio_mm = bill_length_mm / bill_depth_mm
    )
end
```

